title: Putting in work 4v5
body:
had a panth go afk mid game,  he didnt rage or anything i presume his computer just shit itself of something

anyways, more farm for me!

516 cs in 55mins haha

whats the most cs you guys have got? i did get 550 off before but that was in a 120min game so that doesnt really count haha

http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/70613999/200314395

replies.body: 48 minute game hit 600 on karthus and about the same on morde. 300 at 20 minutes is by very best with season 2 wraiths, morde could just use 2 Es and a shield to clear them. so every spawn, free CS. best part was walking into enemy wraiths to get them and just accidently ult for a kill on a low HP jungler like amumu. then come back to lane for another free kill because able to towerdive with that awesome tanky ghost.
i miss being allowed to use morde. such a good jungler in season 4, now he cant do %%%%.
700 or something on zed in a 60 minute game.
917 on Zed before the nerfed his waveclear.

I've got around 300 something CS before in around 40 minutes (I ain't no farmer) but my most recent 4 v 5 game came in here:
http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/70565264/200484578?tab=overview
